  * <li>To bind a shader resource, call <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/api/d3d11/nf-d3d11-id3d11devicecontext-vssetshaderresources">ID3D11DeviceContext::VSSetShaderResources</a>.</li>
  * </ul>
  * 
